-- CBS Sells ‘Good Wife’ Reruns With Internet Viewers First in Line
-- B y   A n d y   F i x m e r
-- 2013-03-13T16:46:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-13/cbs-sells-good-wife-reruns-with-internet-viewers-first-in-line.html
CBS Corp. (CBS)  said it sold rerun rights
to “The Good Wife,” one of broadcast TV’s most popular
programs, in a new arrangement giving Amazon.com’s Web video
customers first access to the show.  The first three seasons of “The Good Wife” will become
available on Amazon Prime Instant Video starting tomorrow, New
York-based CBS said today in a statment. The Hulu service will
get the shows starting in September, while cable’s Hallmark
channel will begin airing the program in January 2014.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andy Fixmer in Los Angeles at 
 afixmer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
